'''Lucas Licensing''' is a wholly owned subsidiary of [[Lucasfilm]] responsible for licensing and merchandising activities related to ''[[Star Wars]]'', [[Wikipedia:Indiana Jones|''Indiana Jones'']] and other Lucasfilm properties. It is unclear if they are still active following [[The Walt Disney Company]]'s acquisition of Lucasfilm.

